{"tid":2315245,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"再有香港人獲得少年JUMP手塚賞佳作！","createTime":"2020-12-07T05:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T16:50:10.000Z","uid":125965,"like":96,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0154b30908c54d538bc767c254f1a1f931ebcf06","tid":2315245,"uid":125965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"香港漫畫家東東獲得第100屆少年JUMP手塚賞海外特別部門佳作！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROcMLpn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROcMLpn.png&h=87ef8b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得上年有位叫楪廷戶ge香港人拎過手塚賞？繼佢之後，再有香港人拎手塚賞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港其實真係有好多好有實力嘅新人漫畫家，希望大家可以多d支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37ccf53bcf944575d90e63f000478d692df858c","tid":2315245,"uid":125965,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"得獎作link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://medibang.com/book/h52008150108573690000449956/view/?fbclid=IwAR2MZGbX5toxkn6lebxdbDzrYfxPHW1G_GhZFp7tyBjOhhY6dZdBEuR1ldI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedibang.com%2Fbook%2Fh52008150108573690000449956%2Fview%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2MZGbX5toxkn6lebxdbDzrYfxPHW1G_GhZFp7tyBjOhhY6dZdBEuR1ldI&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYThF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=541c0076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medibang.com/book/h52008150108573690000449956/view/?fbclid=IwAR2MZGbX5toxkn6lebxdbDzrYfxPHW1G_GhZFp7tyBjOhhY6dZdBEuR1ldI</a>"},{"pid":"8e0eb8c30ed591d906d7c6